{"page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     NCC Services Limited. Trading as NCC Group.\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Business Continuity Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    In the event of an incident affecting NCC Group the analysis of customer needs ensures all of NCC Group\u2019s customers remained informed and updated. The gap analysis will identify areas requiring remediation. It will also help identify any areas which may benefit from improvement.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Detailed consideration of-any-actions perform-during a BCP invocation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Workshops to identify where-each entity fits in-with-the BCP\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Detailed discussions on-the-actions to-be-taken by NCC Group staff-and-its customers\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reviewing ISO22301:2012 to identify compliance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identifying where remediation activities are required\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Teams or individuals will be assigned tasks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Teams report that the remediation is effective\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     The pre-audit highlights any areas which may-not-be-fully compliant.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Qualified Business Continuity expert to-adapt-them for-your context\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Oversight of creation and management of-the-BCMS to-ensure its success.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Keystone of-the operation and maintenance of-the-BCM project\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identified gaps are owned, reported on, checked-and-closed\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     An independent assessment of the state-of-compliance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensures staff are aware of how-to-react in-the-event of an incident\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure the effectiveness of the BCMS\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     The focal point for the project creation and delivery\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensures all relevant staff-and-entities are kept-up-to-date with progress\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Helps to ensure successful outcomes\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3120 per unit per hour\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579474/6062949789597696-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579474/6062949789597696-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579474/6062949789597696-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <spa